invalid type: string "ISSUE: Search bar not working or showing no results.\nCAUSES:\n- Search index corruption.\n- Cortana/SearchUI failure.\n\nRESOLUTION:\n1. Restart Search process:\n   - Task Manager → Details → SearchHost.exe → End task.\n\n2. Rebuild search index:\n   - Control Panel → Indexing Options → Advanced → Rebuild.\n\n3. Reset Windows Search:\n   - PowerShell (Admin):\nN: